Preheat oven to 325 degrees F (165 degrees C). Mix cracker crumbs with SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener and ground cloves, then mix in molasses and melted margarine. In an 8x12 inch baking pan, spread 1/2 apricots and top with 1/2 of the cracker crumb mixture. Repeat. Bake for 50 to 60 minutes, or until bubbly and hot.